	event dispatching, so listeners should only receive those events
	that they requested :-)

2001-11-21  Bill Haneman  <bill.haneman@sun.com>

	* configure.in:
	* docs/Makefile.am:
	* docs/reference:
	* docs/reference:Makefile.am:
	* docs/reference/cspi:
	* docs/reference/cspi:Makefile.am:
